pull.title: gui: Remove unused RPCConsole::tabFocus
pull.body: Added in #14573 but not used, so begone.

events.body: Maybe it's better to comment it out so we can use it if may need it in future (If that's a thing in this project).
IMO better is to kill unused code. It's also easy to bring this back, if needed.
@practicalswift @emilengler please take a new look at [CONTRIBUTING.md#peer-review](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#peer-review), it was recently updated in #16149.
